name: SafariSoundsforSleep
0:

”Alexa stop”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: safari sounds
des: Join us on this African Safari and let the sounds of the beautiful natural landscape lull you to sleep. Get started by saying, 'Alexa, open Safari Sounds,' and enjoy a 30-minute session of sound. It's an excellent feature to use during sleep, for deep relaxation, meditation practices, or to help concentrate on your tasks.
